msgstr "为了节省前端访问的内存，不要注册与内容编辑相关的任何过滤器"

#: classes/PublishPress/Permissions/Constants.php:175
msgid ""
"Attached media do not have any comments, so don't append clauses to comment "
"queries for them"
msgstr "附加媒体没有任何评论，因此不要为它们的评论查询附加条款"

